      "briefTitle": "Prochymal® (Human Adult Stem Cells) Intravenous Infusion Following Acute Myocardial Infarction (AMI)",
      "officialTitle": "A Phase II, Multi-center, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of PROCHYMAL® (Ex Vivo Cultured Adult Human Mesenchymal Stem Cells) Intravenous Infusion Following Acute Myocardial Infarction"
